            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, bash the <strong>lemongrass </strong>with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>tough outer layer<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>of the <strong>lemongrass</strong> and add to the pot with the black rice</p><p>Once the rice is cooked, drain and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1599138047635-x200.jpg",
