      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped lemongrass </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>ginger </strong>(you'll use the rest for your dressing!)</p><p>Drain the<strong> king prawns</strong>,<strong> </strong>then add them to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until everything is cooked through – this is your<strong> lemongrass prawn stir-fry</strong></p>",
